title: Wrist band device holder

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a wrist band device holder, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a perspective view of the wrist band device holder showing my design in use with a phone depicted in broken line;
FIG. 2 is a front view of my design;
FIG. 3 is a left side view of my design;
FIG. 4 is a right side view of my design;
FIG. 5 is a rear elevation view of my design;

The broken line showing of environment in the drawings is for illustrative purposes only and forms no part of the claimed design.
